admin().details: Returns the current admin. Added for external visibility.

changeAdmin(address).details: Changes the admin of the proxy. Can only be called by the current admin. Emits an {AdminChanged} event.

constructor.details: Initializes the proxy with an initial implementation contract and sets the deploying address as the admin.

params.initialAdmin: The address designated as the initial admin.
params.initialImplementation: The address of the initial implementation contract.

implementation().details: Returns the current implementation. Added for external visibility.

upgradeTo(address).details: Upgrades the proxy to a new implementation. Can only be called by the current admin. Emits an {Upgraded} event.

params.newImplementation: Address of the new implementation contract.
